{"tid":1526692,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"前線Ios手足自救神器 - Shortcut","createTime":"2019-09-01T07:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T12:00:02.000Z","uid":79351,"like":61,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"46d4ae7a3136c2d743a60d2410386164fd69a14e","tid":1526692,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"每次有手足被捕都會聯絡唔到律師<br />\n主因係無人知你地已經被捕<br />\n有d醒目d既會係記者面前大叫自己咩名<br />\n但無記者既話就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左盡量避免依個情況<br />\n用Iphone既全部馬上安裝<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先去App Store搵<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Shortcut</span></span><br />\n之後跟足以下步驟一步一步setup<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 1.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvWfk6T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvWfk6T.jpg&h=ec2ec430&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">製作捷徑</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 2.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gozTSdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgozTSdX.jpg&h=46585cf9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSearch message之後按下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳送訊息</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 3.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HNm07Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HNm07Q.jpg&h=e0dbd100&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n收件人就輸入自己信得過既朋友電話<br />\n最好輸入2-3個,以防訓著睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事前記得同人交代聲先<br />\n內容唔好唔好唔好淨係講你已經被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得要留低你中英名全名及身份證number</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得熄左執行時顯示</span></span><br />\n按完成下方<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">設定</span></strong>既icon<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 4.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3swCzuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3swCzuh.jpg&h=c21efaad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加入到Siri</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 5.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnJmgJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnJmgJK.jpg&h=b225fb01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色點</span></span>錄音<br />\n記得唔好派膠set 任何口號<br />\n例如光復香港或時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你個fd多得你條戇鳩唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後右上角完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁不幸被捕只要大叫<br />\n&quot;喂,Siri&quot;之後再叫錄音既指令就會直接send msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出發前要set定同試下次work唔work先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望唔會有人用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A:</span></span><br />\nQ1. 點解叫極Siri都唔應?<br />\nA1. 睇下開左Siri未同埋mon要向上<br />\n<br />\nQ2.現場咁嘈點收音?<br />\nA2.所以最好有Apple Watch. 無既就用你叫口號既力大叫啦<br />\n<br />\nQ3.用parachute有咩分別?<br />\nA3.未用過,手上無資料答你唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好睇完就算,幫手正評同推上熱門</span></span>"},{"pid":"aa059f1cbd3fe466470f278b112b345cdb4969f7","tid":1526692,"uid":79351,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:06:14.000Z","msg":"夢遊完攰到仆街通頂哂左成晚時間研究<br />\n你地竟然唔推實用POST反而推哂D假膠POST上熱門?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75c2837d8a4a5739c24f66259d0ec417630a74a","tid":1526692,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"edff1d10304228b95a586b2f411c9107a17a62b2","tid":1526692,"uid":2343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:09:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bd21649250e16a280274b7eccf18c1bdc8dfd24c","tid":1526692,"uid":307802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:10:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bed1afd55a780a9cec60934867106e854e00570b","tid":1526692,"uid":80866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:11:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccecf2e5d89c03d873701c2367e5d539b3698c35","tid":1526692,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:11:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1f8f9dcfb5b5943bd498c235d1d6707d34927d6","tid":1526692,"uid":210525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:12:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"227b1541c45fe6acd98f7e6c4de5e6330e056dac","tid":1526692,"uid":90839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"又幾好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d55b38908ccd232d7cfe6c30894783cc0313123","tid":1526692,"uid":79351,"like":0,"