ike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46d4ae7a3136c2d743a60d2410386164fd69a14e","tid":1526692,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"每次有手足被捕都會聯絡唔到律師<br />\n主因係無人知你地已經被捕<br />\n有d醒目d既會係記者面前大叫自己咩名<br />\n但無記者既話就...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左盡量避免依個情況<br />\n用Iphone既全部馬上安裝<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">馬上安裝Shortcut</span></span><br />\n<br />\n首先去App Store搵<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Shortcut</span></span><br />\n之後跟足以下步驟一步一步setup<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 1.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MvWfk6T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMvWfk6T.jpg&h=ec2ec430&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">製作捷徑</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 2.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gozTSdX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgozTSdX.jpg&h=46585cf9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\nSearch message之後按下<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳送訊息</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 3.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0HNm07Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0HNm07Q.jpg&h=e0dbd100&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n收件人就輸入自己信得過既朋友電話<br />\n最好輸入2-3個,以防訓著睇唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事前記得同人交代聲先<br />\n內容唔好唔好唔好淨係講你已經被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得要留低你中英名全名及身份證number</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得熄左執行時顯示</span></span><br />\n按完成下方<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">設定</span></strong>既icon<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 4.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3swCzuh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3swCzuh.jpg&h=c21efaad&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">加入到Siri</span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Step 5.</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jnJmgJK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjnJmgJK.jpg&h=b225fb01&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n按<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色點</span></span>錄音<br />\n記得唔好派膠set 任何口號<br />\n例如光復香港或時代革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你個fd多得你條戇鳩唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後右上角完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咁不幸被捕只要大叫<br />\n&quot;喂,Siri&quot;之後再叫錄音既指令就會直接send msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出發前要set定同試下次work唔work先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望唔會有人用到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Q&amp;A:</span></span><br />\nQ1. 點解叫極Siri都唔應?<br />\nA1. 睇下開左Siri未同埋mon要向上<br />\n<br />\nQ2.現場咁嘈點收音?<br />\nA2.所以最好有Apple Watch. 無既就用你叫口號既力大叫啦<br />\n<br />\nQ3.用parachute有咩分別?<br />\nA3.未用過,手上無資料答你唔到<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好睇完就算,幫手正評同推上熱門</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:38:50.000Z","msg":"Parachute 暫時對香港免費，註冊只需要電郵<br />\n都係唔使用手，係add on可以 set 喂siri 嗌口令<br />\n佢一收到口令，馬上黑mon錄影上cloud <br />\n同時有奇怪電話打俾聯絡人<br />\n同時有Text message 俾link 佢睇住你條片<br />\n仲有gps 定位<br />\n<br />\n事後佢會send email畀你，自己查返個電郵都睇得番晒以上紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n佢個app聲稱 made in New York<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"裝哂兩樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得閒研究下Parachute再出教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0fb40bb0de882cab93e048139917efe6b16dbf","tid":1526692,"uid":79351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:40:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"104fcb28ed2e17fa009ef02f6a7d7c4eb797b41b","tid":1526692,"uid":66501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:44:46.000Z","msg":"無iphone 但幫推"},{"pid":"2bab11788022f295cc796e13aa64e5bbbd8b32aa","tid":1526692,"uid":40880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:49:08.000Z","msg":"In Siri we trust"},{"pid":"b11186a3c4726872b4d58f673c7b92d6dd3bda3a","tid":1526692,"uid":302618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T07:52:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E6%258D%25B7%25E5%25BE%2591%2Fid915249334&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=7e6c3213\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E6%258D%25B7%25E5%25BE%2591%2Fid915249334&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=7e6c3213\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapps.apple.com%2Fhk%2Fapp%2F%25E6%258D%25B7%25E5%25BE%2591%2Fid915249334&d=dE5eED8%2BMjLqHtNzOSR2X%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=7e6c3213\" target=\"_blank\">https://apps.apple.com/hk/app/%E6%8D%B7%E5%BE%91/id915249334</a>"},{"pid":"baff6eaf9adbf019d049b03fffef0de7646ec37e","tid":1526692,"uid":293803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:01:44.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到，照推"},{"pid":"bbf4143d429657107ee7e8e3f04bc62c84107111","tid":1526692,"uid":38603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:02:02.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"d6446b30269734859af95c31d8ade5875cb1b2d4","tid":1526692,"uid":110259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:03:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4b84e6b68243f9282616c2fefee5ea059d10634d","tid":1526692,"uid":270296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:07:52.000Z","msg":"push push"},{"pid":"821775ff7fa3710d51790620332f452f51683518","tid":1526692,"uid":14126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T08:24:31.000Z","msg":"Pish"}]}